  <li>+฿50,000 <em>if</em> changing from Business, Education or Volunteer Visa</li>
  <li>Deposit of ฿15,000 held for 1 year (approx. US$490)</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="recurring-costs">Recurring Costs:</h4>
<ul>
  <li>฿11,500 per month, includes taxes and social security (approx. US$370)</li>
</ul>
